---
layout: base.njk
title: "Events"
permalink: /events/
---

<style>
  .events-page { padding: 4rem 2rem 5rem; background: var(--white); }
  .events-inner { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .events-intro { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 3rem; line-height: 1.8; }

  .event-card {
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(167,195,195,0.4);
    border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
  }

  .event-date {
    background: var(--blue);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem; text-align: center;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .event-day { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 1; }
  .event-month { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 0.25rem; opacity: 0.85; }

  .event-body { padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem; background: var(--cream); }
  .event-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .event-desc { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .event-meta { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .event-meta span::before { content: "· "; }
  .event-meta span:first-child::before { content: ""; }

  .events-empty {
    text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(167,195,195,0.08);
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(167,195,195,0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .events-empty h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .events-empty p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }

  .events-contact {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    background: rgba(167,195,195,0.1);
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(167,195,195,0.4);
    border-radius: 4px; padding: 1.75rem;
  }

  .events-contact h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .events-contact p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .event-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .event-date { flex-direction: row; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; justify-content: flex-start; }
  }
</style>

<div class="page-hero">
  <span class="eyebrow">Strandmuschel Rantum · Sylt</span>
  <h1 class="section-title">Events</h1>
</div>

<div class="events-page">
  <div class="events-inner">
    <p class="events-intro">
      Von Livemusik-Abenden über Weinproben bis zu privaten Feiern — die Strandmuschel ist der perfekte Ort für besondere Momente auf der Düne.
    </p>

    <div class="events-empty">
      <h3>Aktuelle Events folgen in Kürze</h3>
      <p>Haltet unsere Seite im Auge oder folgt uns auf Instagram, um keine Ankündigung zu verpassen.<br>
      <a href="{{ site.social.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--black)">@strandmuschel_rantum</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="events-contact">
      <h3>Private Veranstaltungen & Anfragen</h3>
      <p>Ihr möchtet die Strandmuschel für eine Feier, ein Firmenevent oder eine besondere Veranstaltung buchen?
      Meldet euch gerne bei uns — wir freuen uns auf eure Anfrage.<br><br>
      <a href="tel:04651271750" style="color:var(--black)"><strong>{{ site.phone }}</strong></a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" style="color:var(--black)"><strong>{{ site.email }}</strong></a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
